## Functions

- [function] FOO ARG

    Cool! It calls BAR function!

- [function] USER 

- [function] BAR USER

    Cool! This function prints its USER argument of BAR function.

## Classes

- [class] USER

- [reader] USER-NICKNAME USER (= :UNAUTHORIZED)

    User's nickname

- [accessor] USER-EMAIL USER (= NIL)

    User's Email. Can be empty

